{"type":"message","id":"9c180e7e","parentId":"fb787ff2","timestamp":"2026-05-14T10:46:05.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Unity Hub is available at `C:\\Program Files\\Unity Hub\\Unity Hub.exe`. Let me try running it to re-activate the license. But Unity Hub would need GUI interaction.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The license says \"Cannot load ULF license: The digital signature is invalid.\" This is a classic issue with Unity's Chinese versions or when the system time is wrong. \n\nLet me try clearing the licensing client data and re-running. Sometimes deleting the licensing client data and trying again helps.\n\nActually, let me try a completely different approach: use the `Unity.exe -createManualActivationFile` method to get a new license file.\n\nWait, I think I should just notify the user that the Unity license is invalid and needs manual activation. Let me check one more thing - if the Unity Hub app has an updated license stored.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VBnFkqOvNiHvMbBkEHBY5033","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Let's try to kill the licensing cache and re-run\nGet-Process Unity* -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nGet-Process \"Unity Hub\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 2\n\n# Clear licensing client cache\nRemove-Item \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Local\\Unity\\Unity.Licensing.Client.log\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Item \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Local\\Unity\\Unity.Entitlements.Audit.log\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# Try starting Unity Hub to refresh license\nStart-Process \"C:\\Program Files\\Unity Hub\\Unity Hub.exe\" -WindowStyle Minimized\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 5\n\n# Check if Unity Hub started and try to check license status\nGet-Process \"Unity Hub\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Id, ProcessName\nWrite-Host \"Unity Hub started, waiting for license sync...\"\nStart-Sleep -Seconds 10","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":89,"output":472,"cacheRead":19072,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19633,"cost":{"input":0.000012460000000000001,"output":0.00013216,"cacheRead":0.000534016,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000678636}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778755560713,"responseId":"6268042a-6ef0-4c7b-ab2d-6d27eb319788"}}
